<!--Host Website Local Host to Live Server-->

Step1: Export your localhost database

Step2: Make .zip folder your website files (project)

Step3: Open your cPanel and create database (with user previlage)

Step4: Go to phpmyadmin and Import database and update wp_option table with live website link

Step5: Go to File managaer public_html and Import your website files

Step6: Update Database configuration (Database Name, User & Password) in wp_config.php file

Step7: Your Website Live Done!

Just go to Dashboard and set your Permalinks by (Settings > Permalinks > Post name)
